# NAME: Social
# AUTHOR: Kevin (kevshen13)
# REPO: https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# DESCRIPTION: Custom social services rule list for Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-04-04
# MAINTENANCE: Maintain this list by traffic purpose and route behavior.
# RULE: Include social platforms and related domains that should follow the Social policy group.
# RULE: Keep DIRECT-only verification or anti-bot domains in the main config if they should not follow Social.

